OL,3,CSix more people charged following
OL,4,Cviolent unrest over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FHampshire Police have now charged
OL,8,FKevin Reeves, 31, of Portswood Road,
OL,9,FSouthampton; Andrew Riddett, 38, of
OL,10,FSeacombe Green, Southampton; Harry
OL,11,FVarney, 34, of Briarswood,
OL,12,FSouthampton; Taylor Grundy, 22, of
OL,13,FPavillion Way, Gosport; and Dillon
OL,14,FCrawford, 29, of Wilton Avenue,
OL,15,FSouthampton.
OL,17,FAndrew Summerhayes, 38, of Banning
OL,18,FStreet, Romsey, was charged with
OL,19,Fviolent disorder and two counts of
OL,20,Fpossessing an offensive weapon in a
OL,21,Fpublic place, the force added.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
