OL,3,CSix more people charged following
OL,4,Cviolent unrest over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FAll of them will appear at Southampton
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court on Saturday morning.
OL,10,FThe charges come after protests were
OL,11,Fheld in Hampshire city following the
OL,12,Fsentencing of Vickrum Digwa, 23.
OL,14,FHe was jailed for life to serve a
OL,15,Fminimum of 21 years for the murder of
OL,16,F18-year-old Mr Nowak in December.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
