PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780751473
OL,3,CSix more people charged following
OL,4,Cviolent unrest over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FAnger erupted when police body-worn
OL,8,Fvideo was released showing Mr Nowak
OL,9,Fbeing placed in handcuffs moments
OL,10,Fbefore he became unconscious and
OL,11,Fsubsequently died.
OL,13,FThe treatment of the 18-year-old
OL,14,Ftriggered a political row, with the
OL,15,FPrime Minister urging politicians to
OL,16,Fheed the teenager's relatives' calls
OL,17,Fnot to use the case "to cause
OL,18,Fdisturbances".
OL,20,FViolent protests erupted near where
OL,21,Fthe student was fatally stabbed.
OL,26,@yD@UOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
