OL,3,CSix more people charged following
OL,4,Cviolent unrest over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FDigwa had claimed he had been the
OL,8,Fvictim of a racial attack, while Mr
OL,9,FNowak was handcuffed by police who
OL,10,Fignored his pleas he could not breathe
OL,11,Fas he lay dying.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
